'''''[[Nova]]''''' in collaboration with '''''[https://www.instagram.com/upthrust_esports/ Upthrust Esports]''''' presents a BGMI Invitational TDM Championship with India's top teams dubbded the '''''Bhains ki Tait: TDM Battle'''''. The tournament features a prizepool of ₹1,50,000 {{Abbr/INR}}.

==About==
===Broadcast Talent===
{{box|start|padding=1em}}
{{broadcasterCard
|position=Commentator |lang=in
|b1=Nova
|b2=Mayavi
|b3=Hastar
|b4=JankyRor Gaming|b4flag=in
}}
{{box|end}}

===Format===
'''''Bhains Ki Tait: TDM Battle:''' 29th Septmeber 2021 to 2nd October 2021''

'''''Round-1:''' 28th September 2021 to 29th September 2021''
* '' A total of 32 teams will play in Round-1''
* '' Teams will play in a single elimination format.''
* {{bgcolortext|up|''8 Winner teams}} will advance to Round 2.''
<br>
'''''Round-2:''' 30th September 2021''
* '' A total of 16 teams will play in Round-1''
* '' Teams will play in a single elimination format.''
* {{bgcolortext|up|''8 Winner teams}} will advance to the Quarter-Finals.''
<br>
'''''Quarter-Finals:''' 1st October 2021''
* '' A total of 8 teams will play in the Quarter-Finals''.
* '' Teams will be divided into 2 groups and will face off in a round-robin format within their particular group.''
* '' Each team will play a total of 3 matches (12 Matches to be played in total).''
* '' Top 2 teams from each group will qualify for the Semi-Finals
* {{bgcolortext|up|''4 Winner teams}} will advance to the Semi Finals.''
<br>
'''''Semi Finals:''' 2nd October 2021''
* '' A total of 4 teams will play in the Semi Finals''
* '' The 4 teams will face off against each other in a round-robin format''
* '' Each team will play a total of 3 matches (6 Matches to be played in total).''
* {{bgcolortext|up|''Top 2 teams }} from the points table will advance to the Finals.''
* {{bgcolortext|down|''Bottom 2 teams }} from the points table will face off for the 3rd and 4th place.''
<br>
'''''Finals:''' 2nd October 2021''
* '' 2 teams will face off against each other in a BO5 to decide the winner''

