===Format===
* '''League Stage:''' ''June 24th - July 10th, 2022
** Squad {{Abbr/TPP}}, 24 teams.
** '''Week 1 - Launch Week:'''
*** Round-Robin format: 24 teams are drawn into 3 groups.
*** Total 12 matches - 4 matches per day, each team plays a total of 8 matches.
** '''Week 2 & 3:'''
*** '''Weekly Qualifiers:'''
**** Round-Robin format
**** Total 12 matches - 3 matches per day, each team plays a total of 8 matches.
**** {{bgcolortext|up|''Top 16 teams''}} qualify for the ''Weekly Finals''.
*** '''Weekly Finals:'''
**** 16 teams play a total of 12 matches.
** ''Only points of '''Week 1''' and both '''Weekly Finals''' are cumulated towards league standings.
** {{bgcolortext|up|''Top 16 teams''}} advance to ''Finals''.
<div style=margin-top:1em/>
* '''Grand Finals:''' ''July 13th - 17th, 2022
** Squad {{Abbr/TPP}}, Top 16 teams of ''League Stage''.
** 20 matches total, 4 matches per day.
