===Format===
* '''BGMS Season 3:''''' July 19th - August 11th, 2024 at NODWIN Gaming Arena, {{Flag|in}} Delhi NCR
* '''Opening Week:''''' July 19th - 21st, 2024
** 24 teams divided equally into 6 groups of 4 teams.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|20 teams}} directly invited.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|3 teams}} from '''[[TVS Wicked Battles|TVS Qualifier]]'''.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|1 team}} from '''[[Philips OneBlade Cup|OneBlade Qualifier]]'''.
** 3 matchdays , round-robin format.
** 6 matches (2 each day).
*** Each team plays a total of 4 matches.
** '''20 teams''' qualify for the '''League Week'''.
*** {{bgcolortext|up|18 teams}} from the Standings.
*** {{bgcolortext|up|2 teams}} through Audience Choice.
** {{bgcolortext|down|'''Remaining 4 teams'''}} are eliminated.<div style=margin-top:15px></div>
* '''League Week:''''' July 22nd - August 4th, 2024
** 20 teams , 14 matchdays.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|18 teams}} from ''Opening Week''.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|2 teams}} from ''Audience Choice''.<div style=margin-top:10px></div>
** '''Survival Week:''''' July 22nd - 28th, 2024
*** 20 teams divided equally into 5 groups of 4 teams.
*** 7 matchdays , round-robin format.
*** 15 matches (2 each day, 3 on Sunday).
**** Each team plays a total of 12 matches.<div style=margin-top:10px></div>
** '''Domination Week:''''' July 29th - August 4th, 2024
*** 20 teams divided equally into 5 groups of 4 teams.
*** 7 matchdays , round-robin format.
*** 15 matches (2 each day, 3 on Sunday).
**** Each team plays a total of 12 matches.<div style=margin-top:10px></div>
<!--* Total 12 matches - 3 matches each day , each team plays a total of 8 matches-->
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 4 teams}} from the league standings qualify for the '''Finals'''.
** {{bgcolortext|stayup|Remaining teams}} advance to '''Playoffs'''.<div style=margin-top:15px></div>
* '''Playoffs:''''' August 6th - 7th, 2024
** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|16 teams}} from ''League Week'', 2 matchdays.
** 8 matches (4 each day).
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 12 teams}} qualify for the '''Finals'''.<div style=margin-top:15px></div>
* '''Finals:''''' August 9th - 11th, 2024
** 16 teams, 3 matchdays.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|4 teams}} from League Week.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|12 teams}} from Playoffs.
** 12 matches (4 each day).

===Points System===
{{Points10|showtb=true}}
* '''Powerplay''' : Double Points for every elimination in the first phase/zone. <ref name="Powerplay">{{Cite web |url=https://www.instagram.com/reel/C9ZX-QGxNRL|title=Dominate Early, Score Big with Power Play!⚡️Double finish points for each finish in the 1st zone of every match.|date=2024-07-14|publisher='''Nodwin Gaming'''}}</ref>
* '''League Weeks bonuses''' : ''July 22nd - Aug 4th
** '''Bounty''' : 10 points for eliminating the Top 4 teams according to League Standings. <ref name="Bounty">{{Cite web |url=https://www.instagram.com/p/C9ZpuP8yQN1|title=Introducing Bounty in BGMS Season 3! 💥The bounty system will be active during League Week i.e 22 July to 4 August. During this period, teams will have a chance to score more points by eliminating the teams which have a bounty on them.|date=2024-07-14|publisher='''Nodwin Gaming'''}}</ref>
** '''Impact player''' : Double point for every finish secured by the player chosen randomly by a team's IGL before the match (Applicable only on the weekends). <ref name="Impact Player">{{Cite web |url=https://www.instagram.com/p/C9Z2dDNShG8|title=Introducing Impact Player in in BGMS Season 3! 🤩 Squad’s IGL will do a random draw for his squadmates & the chosen player will be considered as the IMPACT PLAYER & double finish points will be awarded for each finishes done by that player.|date=2024-07-14|publisher='''Nodwin Gaming'''}}</ref>

