===Format===
* '''Pre Quarter Finals:''''' November 4th - 7th, 2024
** 64 teams, 4 matchdays.
*** 32 invited team.
*** 32 from Open Qulifier.
** Teams are divided equally into 4 groups of 16.
** Each group will play 6 matches in 4 days.
** Top 8 team from each group (Total 32 teams) advance to Quarter Finals.
<div style="margin-top:12px"></div>
* '''Quarter Finals:''''' November 8th - 9th, 2024
** 32 teams, 2 matchdays.
** Teams are divided equally into 2 groups of 16.
** Each group will play 6 matches in 4 days.
** Top 12 team from each group (Total 24 teams) advance to Semi Finals.
<div style="margin-top:12px"></div>
* '''Semi Finals:''''' November 10th - 11th, 2024
** 24 teams, 2 matchdays.
** Teams are divided equally into 3 groups of 8.
** Each group will play 8 matches in 2 days.
** Round-robin format.
** Top 16 teams advance to the Grand Finals.
<div style="margin-top:12px"></div>
* '''Grand Finals:''''' November 12th - 14th, 2024
** 16 teams, 3 matchdays.
** 18 matches (6 each day).

