'''Battlegrounds Mobile India Series 2026''' or '''BGIS 2026''' is the fifth edition of ''[[Battlegrounds Mobile India Series|Battlegrounds Mobile India Series]]''. The tournament is organized by '''[https://www.krafton.com/en/ KRAFTON]''' and features a total prize pool of ₹4,00,00,000 {{Abbr/INR}}.

==About==
===Format===
* '''League Stage:''''' Jan 26th - Mar 8th, 2026
**{{TextDropdown|title=For League Stage format|section=LeagueStage|width=max-content}}
* '''Round 1:''''' Jan 26th - Feb 1st, 2026
** 1024 Teams, 8 matchdays.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|1016 Teams}} from In-Game Qualifiers.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|Bottom 8 Teams}} from The Grind Group D.
** Teams divided into 64 groups with 16 Teams in each group.
** Each team plays a total of 6 matches.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 7 Teams}} from each group + {{bgcolortext|up|Top 48 Teams}} among the remaining teams (Total 496 Teams) qualify for ''Round 2.

* '''Round 2:''''' Feb 5th - 8th, 2026
** 512 Teams, 4 matchdays.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|496 Teams}} from Round 1.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|Top 8 Teams}} from The Grind Group D.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|Bottom 8 Teams}} from The Grind Group C.
** Teams are divided into 32 groups with 16 Teams in each group.
** Each team plays a total of 6 matches.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 7 Teams}} from each group + {{bgcolortext|up|Top 16 Teams}} among the remaining teams (Total 240 Teams) qualify for ''Round 3.

* '''Round 3:''''' Feb 12th - 15th, 2026
** 256 Teams, 4 matchdays.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|240 Teams}} from Round 2.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|Top 8 Teams}} from The Grind Group C.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|Bottom 8 Teams}} from The Grind Group B.
** Teams are divided into 16 groups with 16 Teams in each group.
** Each team plays a total of 6 matches.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 6 Teams}} from each group + {{bgcolortext|up|Top 16 Teams}} among the remaining teams (Total 112 Teams) qualify for ''Round 4.

* '''Round 4:''''' Feb 19th - 22nd, 2026
** 128 Teams, 4 matchdays.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|112 Teams}} from Round 3.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|Top 8 Teams}} from The Grind Group B.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|Bottom 8 Teams}} from The Grind Group A.
** Teams are divided into 8 groups with 16 Teams in each group.
** Each team plays a total of 6 matches.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 7 Teams}} from each group (Total 56 Teams) advance to ''Quarter Finals.
** {{bgcolortext|stay|Top 8 Teams}} among the remaining teams advance to ''Wildcard.

* '''Quarter Finals:''''' Feb 26th - Mar 1st, 2026
** 64 Teams, 4 matchdays.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|56 Teams}} from Round 4.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|Top 8 Teams}} from The Grind Group A.
** Teams are divided into 4 groups with 16 Teams in each group.
** Each team plays a total of 6 matches.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 16 Teams}} based on the cumulative overall standings advance to ''Semi Finals.
** {{Bgcolortext|stay|17th - 40th placed teams}} (24 teams) advance to ''Wildcard.

* '''Wildcard:''''' Mar 5th - 8th, 2026
** 32 Teams, 4 matchdays.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|24 Teams}} from Quarter Finals.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|8 Teams}} from Round 4.
** Teams are divided into 4 groups with 8 Teams in each group.
** Round-robin format.
** Each team plays a total of 12 matches.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 8 Teams}} based on the cumulative overall standings advance to ''Semi Finals.
{{TextDropdown|end}}

* '''Semi Finals:''''' Mar 12th - 15th, 2026 at Sandhya Convention Center, {{Flag|in}} Hyderabad
** 24 Teams, 4 matchdays.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|16 Teams}} from Quarter Finals.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|8 Teams}} from Wildcard.
** Teams are divided into 3 groups with 8 Teams in each group.
** Double Round-robin format.
** Each team plays a total of 16 matches.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 8 Teams}} advance to ''Grand Finals.
** {{bgcolortext|stay|Remaining 16 Teams}} proceed to ''Survival Stage.

* '''Survival Stage:''''' Mar 16th - 17th, 2026 at Sandhya Convention Center, {{Flag|in}} Hyderabad
** 16 Teams, 2 matchdays.
** 12 matches (6 each day).
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 8 Teams}} advance to ''Grand Finals''.

* '''Grand Finals:''''' Mar 27th - 29th, 2026 at Chennai Trade Centre, {{Flag|in}} Chennai
** 16 Teams, 3 matchdays.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|8 teams}} from Semi Finals.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|8 teams}} from Survival Stage.
** 18 matches (6 each day).

