===Allocations===
* {{Bgcolortext|up|'''Top 8 teams'''}} from ''Group A'' qualify for {{LeagueIconSmall/battlegrounds mobile india series}} '''[[Battlegrounds_Mobile_India_Series/2026| BGIS 2026: Quarter Finals]]'''
* {{Bgcolortext|up|'''Top 8'''}} from ''Group B'' & {{Bgcolortext|stayup|'''Bottom 8'''}} from ''Group A'' qualify for {{LeagueIconSmall/battlegrounds mobile india series}} '''[[Battlegrounds_Mobile_India_Series/2026| BGIS 2026: Round 4]]'''
* {{Bgcolortext|up|'''Top 8'''}} from ''Group C'' & {{Bgcolortext|stayup|'''Bottom 8'''}} from ''Group B'' qualify for {{LeagueIconSmall/battlegrounds mobile india series}} '''[[Battlegrounds_Mobile_India_Series/2026| BGIS 2026: Round 3]]'''
* {{Bgcolortext|up|'''Top 8'''}} from ''Group D'' & {{Bgcolortext|stayup|'''Bottom 8'''}} from ''Group C'' qualify for {{LeagueIconSmall/battlegrounds mobile india series}} '''[[Battlegrounds_Mobile_India_Series/2026| BGIS 2026: Round 2]]'''
* {{Bgcolortext|stay|'''Bottom 8 teams'''}} from ''Group D'' qualify for {{LeagueIconSmall/battlegrounds mobile india series}} '''[[Battlegrounds_Mobile_India_Series/2026| BGIS 2026: Round 1]]'''

